Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling wide to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:13.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:24.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}But it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:34.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:42.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the times we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:50.74,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That the words in our hands we will draw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:58.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Maybe it wasn't 'cause\N you're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:10.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Every moment, everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:15.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can feel, I can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:20.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding you from bad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:27.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You will learn
